==续作==
{{Main article|古墓丽影：暗影}}
于Gamescom 2015，史克威尔艾尼克斯无意中透露，自2013年重新启动的古墓丽影系列作品共有三款。也就是说除了已在2013年发售的《古墓丽影》、2015年发售的《古墓丽影：崛起》之外，开发商还将推出最后一款游戏作为三部曲的终结之作<ref name="GameSpot">{{cite web |last=Makuch |first=Eddie |date=2015-08-06 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/square-enix-weighs-in-on-rumored-rise-of-the-tomb-/1100-6429532/ |title=Square Enix Weighs in on Rumored Rise of the Tomb Raider Sequel |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2015-08-06 |archive-date=2019-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015152022/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/square-enix-weighs-in-on-rumored-rise-of-the-tomb-/1100-6429532/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.gamersky.com/news/201508/631040.shtml|title = 新《古墓丽影》确定为三部曲 《古墓丽影：崛起》之后还有最后一作|accessdate = 2015-09-05|author = |date = |publisher = 游民星空|language = zh-cn|archive-date = 2019-10-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191016022355/https://www.gamersky.com/news/201508/631040.shtml|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2018年3月15日，史克威尔艾尼克斯正式公布 《[[古墓丽影：暗影|古墓丽影：暗影]]》，这将是重启系列的第三部也是最后一部作品。游戏将于2018年9月14日登陆PlayStation 4、Xbox One和Microsoft Windows平台。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2018/3/15/17123806/shadow-of-the-tomb-raider-teaser-trailer-xbox-one-ps4-pc |title=Shadow of the Tomb Raider Teaser Trailer |date=2018-03-15 |website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] |access-date=2018-03-15 |archive-date=2018-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315190609/https://www.polygon.com/2018/3/15/17123806/shadow-of-the-tomb-raider-teaser-trailer-xbox-one-ps4-pc |dead-url=no }}</ref>
